dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 2 meter contours, hachures, land form drawings, and spot heights. Depth shown by isobaths and soundings. Prime meridian is Paris. Diégo-Suarez name change to Antsiran̈ana Includes diagram of sheet assembly and cartographic responsibility. "Héliogravure du Service géographique de Madagascar (1935)."
